Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可爱了～～～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是小金悄悄的好好的拍下来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张是直接用手抓东西吃的雏莓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张是翠星石换衣服的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让她发现而稍微费了点事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇少女的人偶们…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～要是大家能马上来我家里就好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:01:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也该认真起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之  现在还是应该慎重的步步为营吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样  像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要每个地方都揉到是诀窍的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揉了一圈又一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做出好吃的饼干来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  小雏做得真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  要不要一起来做饼干？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有用的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红不可能来做的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会拿「不要  会把裙子弄脏的」\N之类的理由拒绝的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  就像我说的一样的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一大跳的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红竟然自己说要来做饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是吹的什么风的说？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只…只是心血来潮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有什么别的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不过  真红穿围裙好适合哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我要做些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那就来揉面团吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——我看不下去了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这成什么样子的说嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个饼干的面团而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想要违抗我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…好大的烟哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么的说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第…第一次做总会不顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好了！快把窗户打开！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过456次失败后总算等到这一天了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们见识见识小金真正的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——真  真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是金丝雀哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来做什么的说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小金是来…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正…正好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都在这里  就趁着这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我认真地来做你们的对手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  烤好了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饼干做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有这个机会  一起尝尝如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来我最完美的杰作已经烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪  把我的饼干端上来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是翠星石做的看起来最好吃的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏的花蛋饼干也烤得很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…什么？猪吗？…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真失礼！这是库库啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库库？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没想到事情会进展成这种形式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超出我的考虑范围了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…你到底在想什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  小金丝雀  趁热吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是小雏做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该…该不会  在这个饼干里做了什么手脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃吧…嘻嘻嘻…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我…我可不会上你们的当！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道说  真正的圈套在这红茶里面？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  不知怎么突然很想睡觉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于睡着了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁着现在  拿走这个家伙的蔷薇圣母的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还自称什么谋士  真可笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  笨蛋笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种小伎俩对我蔷薇少女中第一的头脑派金丝雀…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来呀来呀  这些也吃掉的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难吃——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个饼干是真红做的的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「果然」是什么意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也拼命去做了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下…下次一定会更好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真红…有点…奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也不错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？这就要回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就这样放过你们吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定会把你们都击败的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下次就烤些司康饼等着你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:03.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(scone：一种英式风味的小型圆饼  制作较为简单)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛！真红完全把我当傻瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金丝雀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这次要邀请我去野餐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和真红不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以告诉我一件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想要和我们战斗么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此你又想怎么样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你是这个意思的话就没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  有一件事请你记住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行爱丽丝游戏之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会有人离开我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会再回到现在这个样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事你不说我也知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——？真红她们烤饼干？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊  这都能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要吃真红做的比较好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是大家来我家里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要和她们一起做饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后让她们穿各种各样的服装
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍很多很多照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——光是想着就——
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得到她们的话  就一定要胜出爱丽丝游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果这么做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行爱丽丝游戏之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会有人离开我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会再回到现在这个样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  小美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…如果  小金不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小金不能动了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  变成那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有小金的日子我过不下去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会死掉的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷  冷静点  小美！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不愿意！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金要一直陪在我身边！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样  就不能对她们听之任之了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不战斗的话  就没法得到她们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀——摩擦生热让脸烧起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊……今天要住下来的说吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.83,0:10:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷他们在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石  你在做什么的说？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:34.72,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}夢の中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:42.61,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}生まれた心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}诞生于梦中的心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:47.20,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}カラス窓が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:51.25,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}君見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}玻璃窗上映出你的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:57.59,chaquriwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}瞬のウチに込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}在一瞬间充满心胸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠  今天心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又没吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿我再来拿  至少要吃一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为只要唱歌我就会来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像傻瓜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你来了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…原来如此  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学习吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？…啊  是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来得正好  现在可以看到好东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧  让他们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正要赋予那个人偶「生命」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「生命」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会动了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面为大家播放各地送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀罕的影像和各种活动的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大花园～喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻嘻…活该的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说谎  我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几天你明显的改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而应该说是「察觉到了」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「察觉到了」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该做什么  我想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…想做的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金丝雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始爱丽丝游戏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一乐章  攻击之华尔兹！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点莓！快点给我起来的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是第二乐章！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追击的巴洛克！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌！耳朵好难受哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！金丝雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:14:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家不发火你就乱搞一气！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拨弦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪斯科！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该结束了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金丝雀  快停下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀！快放开！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我饶不了你的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要毁掉你的小提琴的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲剧的变奏曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们承认失败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且今后听从我的命令的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我停手也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我们会乖乖的服从你的说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  所以我才要打倒你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:15:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了小美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定要取得胜利！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终乐章  破坏之交响曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快停手的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金…金丝…雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是认真的  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠这些花瓣是没办法挡住我的声音的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这样又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我收拾好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个被你搞得一团乱的房间  快点收拾好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我我我知道了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…樱田小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总  总算是做完了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！这叫自作自受的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是对翠星石等人无礼的惩罚的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你想把我们打倒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了小美…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美想要得到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小美小姐得到我们之后想要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩  一起做饭  换衣服什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这个问题就能够解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  这件事刚才已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  资料已经通过邮件确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我再好好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？喂喂？喂喂？怎么了？然后呢？然后…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…？喂喂——？喂喂——？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  小美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金把她们带回来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是跟你一起来了而已的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是小美小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是做梦而是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是真正的好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊  这个这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是为了让大家来的时候穿而买的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来穿上吧来穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  让我拍照！拜托了～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来别碰我别靠近我的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒  好棒  太棒了  各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说这也太放任她了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红～翠星石～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最棒了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是金丝雀的媒介呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看得出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏好高兴哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…是吗？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…人类真是什么样的都有的说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真感动！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都眼花缭乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美是摄影的专家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多其它的衣服想让你们穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要拍很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  玩的真高兴哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  被她好好的摆弄了一通的说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:20:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你没有战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有战斗的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  金丝雀是来进行爱丽丝游戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望战斗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是宿命的话还是会的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再失去什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我不会再战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要放弃爱丽丝游戏吗  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.54,0:22:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！那是翠星石平时坐的地方的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我才不管吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.81,0:23:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我蔷薇少女中第一的头脑派金丝雀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.50,0:23:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想坐在这里就要可以坐在这里吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…你这个小不点人偶！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:23:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么任性的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石也说点什么的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:24:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？苍星石  不在的说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯也不在吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.71,0:24:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  蔷薇少女  梦见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.23,0:24:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旋律宛如梦中所见吧？
